{
  "texts": [
    "User Needs ExtractionSoftware development is conducted based on the requirements of stakeholders such as end-users, system administrators, and development companies [21].",
    "In particular, in the development of services tailored to users, users represent a critical stakeholder group, and their needs become paramount [22].",
    "However, conducting direct needs assessments with many end-users presents challenges.Our prior research has tackled the automatic extraction of user needs based on dialogue as shown in Fig. 1 [9].",
    "Traditionally, the task of eliciting requirements, performed by experts, is undertaken by VAs.",
    "The VA's backend operates a needs extraction system, which analyzes the needs and generates response statements."
  ]
}